果你個本夠多 做幾部機嘅台主分返個風險正正常都有萬幾蚊嘅<br />\n<br />\n利申9up"},{"pid":"77180524f4a7475b0fbbe644ba670e8f666bf369","tid":1969260,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T20:11:51.000Z","msg":"冇，講真真係打個和<br />\n果日好彩嘅可以食到個開心樂園餐<br />\n不過賺唔賺都唔係重點<br />\n重點係我想將夾公仔嘅歡樂送比大家"},{"pid":"d524807d4af1add41ae27dcc43736ad0cba62bda","tid":1969260,"uid":354348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T20:16:13.000Z","msg":"呢們生意唔好do lol<br />\n香港人潛意識覺得夾公仔🧸俾人昆<br />\n一次$10,仲要次次夾唔到<br />\n你估你呢度係台灣🇹🇼"},{"pid":"4893c4d8e6fe8b9da918c3ec2465e38ff8cb3174","tid":1969260,"uid":16113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T20:18:11.000Z","msg":"業主：乜鳩都唔理總之租地方出去同收租，risk 係無人租地方<br />\n<br />\n場主：要交地方每月租金同買機嘅成本（one-off), 收入係租機出去嘅錢，risk 自然係驚無人租機要自己頂租同埋耐啲回本<br />\n<br />\n台主：要交部機每月租金，但賺幾多自己袋，risk 係無人玩，要自己頂租金，但unlimited profit<br />\n<br />\n做場主個班，擺明就係有筆錢又覺得夾公仔機係開始hit, 但又想limit 個risk (當然都limit 埋個profit) 所以租出去比人做台主<br />\n<br />\n講到尾都係睇你對夾公仔個熱潮幾有信心同有無一筆起手嘅資金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf63b0ce8fb5c54b544035e04c1c6d35508c1bdd","tid":1969260,"uid":248351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"726573938dfcca0a3ec50082b978b4d828ab3999","tid":1969260,"uid":74598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T18:50:26.000Z","msg":"我都想每個月比5500學下做台主學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細b一直冇賺我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你都on9既 一部機成本6000千 2個月回本咁都話蝕住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T20:24:06.000Z","msg":"鋪租？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc3e37fda482541d3a4bacd01f4c1231a7d678b","